text: How about it? Did you find any photos you liked?

...Ah, s-sorry. I, uh, ended up looking at photos
of Hiori-chan and Meguru-chan...

Haha, the shoots were separate,
so it's fine to take your time and look.

Both of them look so radiant and lovely in the
photos... They're really wonderful...

Mano, you shine just as brightly as the two of them.
You worked really hard during the shoot.

I can't wait to see the three of you
on stage wearing these outfits.
...I'd be happy if you felt that way.

I'll do my best to stand alongside
them properly from now on...
